{"tid":663263,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"13-5-2018，雲加 在遊蕩裡 在球場裡 突然便老去","createTime":"2018-05-13T07:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T08:56:05.000Z","uid":36497,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55d199b89248c7688000c12d1707c0b267f2e6ea","tid":663263,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"雲加可否不要老 伴我長高<br />\n雲加可否不要老 伴我征討<br />\n雲加 即使早知 真相那味道<br />\n卻想完美到 去違抗定數<br />\n<br />\n04全部也不倒<br />\n高層以後也安好<br />\n最好 我在意的 任何面容都 不會老<br />\n<br />\n為何 在遊蕩裡 在球場裡 突然便老去<br />\n談好 一個事情 可以兌現時 雲加已安睡<br />\n祈求 雲加萬歲 舊情萬歲 別隨便老去<br />\n高層 這個壞人 偏卻決絕如許<br />\n停留耐些 也不許<br />\n<br />\n雲加可否不要老 再領風騷<br />\n雲加可否不要老 另創新高<br />\n人生 恍恍惚惚 走到這段路<br />\n也只能靠你 去提我未老<br />\n<br />\n04年月有多好<br />\n怎麼以後碰不到<br />\n那些 已白髮的 就如在無聲 的控訴<br />\n<br />\n雲加 在遊蕩裡 在遊玩裡 突然便老去<br />\n談好 一個事情 可以兌現時 你又已安睡<br />\n祈求 舊人萬歲 雲加萬歲 別隨便老去<br />\n時光 這個壞人 偏卻冷酷如許<br />\n離場慢些 也不許<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae730460a1ee4899c8199bfcac6f651f7b7238cb","tid":663263,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0c6a872c2275db5e5a8717b49062cbf443d77d","tid":663263,"uid":49065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},{"pid":"ef889354067eab51f9e9f559d5b45663811c96e5","tid":663263,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e032a444a266984fd1c48446d973e8bdfbd9007c","tid":663263,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef889354067eab51f9e9f559d5b45663811c96e5","tid":663263,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/bi